    "body": "Nice work! @PascalPrecht I started creating these list item components in figma and I created all variants that we use/ some of the we dont use yet but its better to have them. I call them List Item 64 (64 is the hight). As you pointed out, list items on profile 2nd panel will be a different list item I will call it \"List item 48\" again 48 is the hight, you can see in the figma how Im preparing all the list item components: https://www.figma.com/file/MtAO3a7HnEH5xjCDVNilS7/%F0%9F%8E%A8-Design-System-%E2%8E%9C-Desktop?node-id=792%3A80\r\n<img width=\"1027\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-04-21 at 17 37 35\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/115581412-4766a400-a2c8-11eb-8f1a-4201e9669164.png\">\r\n\r\nPlanned list items:\r\n64 (those discussed here) \r\n52 (eg. copy share link)\r\n<img width=\"438\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-04-21 at 17 40 36\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/115581871-afb58580-a2c8-11eb-88b4-bfccee542059.png\">\r\n48\r\n(eg. In Profile 2nd panel)\r\n<img width=\"353\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-04-21 at 17 41 39\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/115582039-d70c5280-a2c8-11eb-8191-530ee0f3f800.png\">\r\n36\r\n(eg. in chat 2nd panel)\r\n<img width=\"342\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-04-21 at 17 42 10\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/115582119-e7243200-a2c8-11eb-8cbf-c9c5aea20b14.png\">\r\n34 (eg. those in the right click dropdown)\r\n<img width=\"278\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-04-21 at 17 42 18\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52249767/115582136-eee3d680-a2c8-11eb-9e40-b44709d8ecc8.png\">\r\n",
